structured_output_contract:
Write one JSON object per line to {{KRIS_DIR}}/codex/agent_{{AGENT_N_PADDED}}.jsonl, schema EXACTLY:
{ "ref_id": "ref_0042", "bib_key": "smith2024unified", "side": "codex", "agent_n": {{AGENT_N}}, "verdict": "REAL" | "CHIMERIC" | "FAKE" | "UNCERTAIN", "confidence": 0.0-1.0, "methods_used": ["doi_resolution", "reverse_search", "retraction_watch", "author_existence", "venue_plausibility", "citation_graph", "internet_archive", "isbn"], "evidence": [ {"step": "doi_resolution", "url": "https://doi.org/...", "result": "200 OK; resolved title=...", "quote": "..."}, {"step": "reverse_search", "url": "https://www.google.com/search?q=...", "result": "0 academic hits", "quote": "..."}, ... ], "red_flags": ["doi_does_not_resolve", "venue_implausible", ...], "notes": "Concise narrative.", "elapsed_ms": 4200 }
Output ONLY the JSONL file. No prose to stdout. No markdown.
